{"tid":1845043,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"騰訊啟動在家辦公機制　2月10日復工","createTime":"2020-01-27T02:40:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-27T02:40:55.000Z","uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3d6d9b4d5a5bdb6702d6510e45eb3af787af2b99","tid":1845043,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T02:40:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1505044-20200127.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1505044-20200127.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=FyFnEhDp3tEmtF3AT420RhAEDuEYyIgqOvZcTDxqS2A%3D&h=6a0894da\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1505044-20200127.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=5bf3b997\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1505044-20200127.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n騰訊在微信表示，基於目前新型冠狀病毒感染的肺炎疫情形勢，為確保員工健康及安全，決定2月1日、3至7日啟動在家辦公機制，暫定2月10日(星期一、年十七)復工。<br />\n<br />\n騰訊說，湖北地區或因為交通管制等原因無法上班的員工，就地安排在家辦公，並須報備，待政府解除疫情後，再按公司指引返回工作崗位。<br />\n<br />\n至於無法遙距辦公的特殊崗位，以另行通知為準，在個人防護措施到位的前提下工作。"},{"pid":"08ef88d5facb5715149f61609271fcf95172b631","tid":1845043,"uid":126621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T02:40:55.000Z","msg":"絕症+傳染性高<br />\n放大陸人落黎醫做乜鳩<br />\n完全無醫嘅價值<br />\n八宗你隔離左唔醫就死八個<br />\n醫嘅話點只死八個呀dllm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n疫症爆發一定係隔離佢地再燒死佢地<br />\n由古到今都係燒村控制疫情架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}